{"tid":1960704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥本財政年度加薪12萬 特首辦：適時回應！","createTime":"2020-04-06T10:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T02:11:38.000Z","uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"09185eb82dfe2452f9ca29d758ce29f2d02ee3ad","tid":1960704,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1857c02c20bd03d73f2e957ac79e2b19856b4e","tid":1960704,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥今個財政年度的年薪預算增加十二萬，有議員要求減薪與市民共渡時艱。特首辦指若情況轉差，會適時回應。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員田北辰：「這個時勢，怎可能有任何機構管理層一把手能厚面皮加人工？」<br />\n<br />\n特首辦常任秘書長林雪麗：「加薪是去年七月一日按既定機制，按消費物價指數上調少少。為齊心抗疫，特首與問責團隊捐一個月薪金予公益金，希望幫助有需要人士。特首仍提過往後情況繼續轉差，問責團隊會作出適當回應。」<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員容海恩：「最壞時段仍未到，何時才算繼續轉差？你要見到有人死？市民繼續確診？數字漸多？」<br />\n<br />\n林雪麗：「我相信特首及問責團隊都會深思這個問題，適時作出回應。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=386903\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D386903&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=7e865106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D386903&h=fcaf38b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=386903</a>"},{"pid":"46698eae9c37190b49de73c47b094c382a87e1a6","tid":1960704,"uid":65091,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yv6B4Nq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYv6B4Nq.gif&h=cda2fa07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9348e06634f77d5d706ea00f3a05e7940dcf828a","tid":1960704,"uid":62532,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"林鄭班子政府成功團結大多香港人 <br />\n抵加人工啦"},{"pid":"bba17e1be7760f5a719b2f99a5117251314031af","tid":1960704,